The [[adjective]] verrueckt means [[crazy]] or [[mad]] in [[German]]. This word is commonly used by [[beginner]] [[German]] learners as a [[slang]] [[term]] to poke fun at each other. Otherwise, it is also used by [[German]] speakers to scold non-speakers [[without]] their [[knowledge]].

